Sure, here are some example sentences using the Serbian word "trke" (races):

1. *Trke* su uzbudljive za gledanje. (Races are exciting to watch.)
2. Učestvujem u mnogim *trkama* tokom godine. (I participate in many races throughout the year.)
3. On je veliki ljubitelj konjskih *trka*. (He is a big fan of horse races.)
4. Svake nedelje održavaju se auto *trke* na ovoj stazi. (Auto races are held on this track every week.)
5. Volim da pratim sportske *trke* na televiziji. (I enjoy watching sports races on TV.)
6. *Trke* su popularne u mnogim delovima sveta. (Races are popular in many parts of the world.)
7. Ove godine planiram da odem na moto *trke* u Italiju. (This year, I plan to go to the motorcycle races in Italy.)
8. Moraš se prijaviti na vreme ako želiš da učestvuješ u *trkama*. (You have to sign up on time if you want to participate in races.)

I hope this helps!